tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE DemographicData (
    data_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    citizen_id INT,
    occupation VARCHAR(50),
    residence_status VARCHAR(20),
    FOREIGN KEY (citizen_id) REFERENCES Citizens(citizen_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Demographics (
  demographic_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  citizen_id INT,
  population INT,
  median_age INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (citizen_id) REFERENCES Citizens(citizen_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Addresses (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  city VARCHAR(50),
  state VARCHAR(50),
  zip_code VARCHAR(10),
  citizen_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (citizen_id) REFERENCES Citizens (id)
);

CREATE TABLE Languages (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  language_name VARCHAR(50),
  fluency_level VARCHAR(20),
  citizen_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (citizen_id) REFERENCES Citizens (id)
);

CREATE TABLE citizen_history (
  history_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  citizen_id INT,
  registration_date DATE,
  status VARCHAR(20),
  FOREIGN KEY (citizen_id) REFERENCES citizens(citizen_id)
);
